QuestData.Title: Nath'raxas Hold: Rescue Mission
QuestData.Description: Your forces are adequately equipped for the mission to save my people from Nath'raxas. Order your champions to bolster my assault, and together we will dismantle the Legion's stranglehold over the region.
QuestData.LogDescription: Use the Scouting Map and complete the mission, "Nath'raxas Breakout".
